Table 1407/1 - WEAPON TYPE, GENERIC (1-30)

 

Related Documents:

None

 

Sponsor:

None

 

Unit of Measure:

 

 

WEAPON TYPE, GENERIC

Instructive - Allowable Entries (1-30)

Explanation

Alphabetic Upper Case (A-Z), Blank, Numeric (0-9), Special

ARMAMENT TYPE-CODES FROM ATP-29  OR LITERAL WHEN NOT APPLICABLE.

Regular Expression

[-\.,\(\)\?A-Z 0-9]{1,30}
